				I started this quest by reading the posts.  When I spotted a 50 necro bagging shadowed men in commons, I stopped to ask if I could loot the shining stone.  Half an hour later, I'm on my way with it and get it enchanted twice, at the gypsy camp in Rathe Mts and in Highpass.  On to Cazic, where I wait in the courtyard on Radiant.  I stay busy buffing the groups there with alacrity.  When Radiant is slain, I get the loot and thanks from the groups there.  I'd prefer to go and kill my own mobs, but I'm in a small guild and it's hard to find a group at times.  When I can't get in, I wait and buff and help as I can.  Most groups appreciate this and are happy to help me get my ENCH-only items that they don't need.
